    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_7549eca8-2226-4fdf-a584-d6f79b038d0b" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If enabled in your student's course, you can use Announcements Redesign to participate in course announcements.</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>If Announcements Redesign is not available in your student's course, it has not been enabled by your student's instructor.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-discussions" data-step-uuid="01638ea6-e952-478e-ae2d-28930944d133">
    <h2 id="open-discussions" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Announcements</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/598/088/original/8a6981f3-511f-4825-b67e-42723c39ed6c.png" srcset="" alt="Open Announcements" height="230" width="154">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_34ce63a0-8ac3-45bc-9429-e324805c1b38" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To view class announcements, click the <strong>Announcements</strong> link in Course Navigation.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-discussion" data-step-uuid="5aaef5c4-8275-481f-ae28-7436e0060177">
